  <div class="row">
    <div class="container mb-2 frostedglass col">
      <p class="text-center runguszone mt-1" style="font-size:135%">Some RT YouTube Channels were also backed up on Ragtag Archive. <br>
        <a class="alert-link" href="https://roosteretal-archive.ragtag.moe/">Click here to check it out!</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="container mb-2 frostedglass col">
      <p class="text-center runguszone mt-1 mb-1" style="font-size:135%">The vast majority of content is now on Internet Archive, but still needs to be organized!</p>
      <p class="text-center runguszone mt-1 mb-1" style="font-size:135%">In the meantime, checkout the <a class="alert-link" href="/playlists">Playlists page</a> for archived content from YouTube</p>
      <p class="text-center runguszone mt-1 mb-1" style="font-size:135%">Or, try finding what you're looking for on our <a class="alert-link" href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/17Vqd_xYLh-xma_nw_TkeFexzQ2sZ4uEntibiZB8KlRI/view" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Archival Checklist!</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</pagelogo>
